title: Two bedroom apartment available - Income restrictions apply
posting_body: ['Summerfield apartments has a two bedroom apartment available in early June.', 'This unit is income restricted and so you would need to make under the amount listed below depending on how many people are moving into the apartment.', 'Call for more details or to set up a showing -', 'show contact info', '.', 'Income must be below the following limits based on # of household members in the unit.', '1 person - $35,250 Annually', '2 people - $40,250 Annually', '3 people - $45,300 Annually', '4 people - $50,300 Annually', '5 people - $54,350Annually', '6 people - $58,350 Annually', 'Some additional information about Summerfield-', '*Heat, water, and garbage are included in monthly rent', '*Garages are available for $60/month', '*On-site card operated laundry in each building', "*Security Deposits are the same amount as first month's rent; pending background/ credit check.", '*Leases are offered on a minimum of 12-month basis.', '*Pet policy: We allow 1 cat per household; with approved vaccinations, spayed/ neutered, a $300 deposit, and a $20 pet rent.', 'Sorry no dogs.']
